def splitElements(xs:String):Seq[String] = {
    xs.split(" ").map((x:String) => x.split("-")(0))
}

val splitElementsUDF = udf(splitElements _)

csvSequencesDF
    .withColumn("sequenceList", splitElementsUDF($"sequence"))
    .drop("sequence")
    .write.mode("overwrite").parquet(SEQUENCES_PARQUET_FILENAME)

def toListString(valuesList:Seq[org.apache.spark.sql.Row]): String = {
    "[" + valuesList.aggregate("")(
        (text:String, row:org.apache.spark.sql.Row) => row(0).toString + ", " + text,
        (text1, text2) => text1 + ", " + text2) + "]"
}

val counts = toListString(metadata.where("count > 1 AND count < 500")
    .select("count").collect())

val labelsAvg = toListString(metadata.select("labels").collect())
    
val maxCount = metadata.where("count < 500").take(1)(0)(2)
z.show(metadata.where("count > 100"))
